  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Orthopedic implant contact stress credibility assessment (NC-4 clean)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA contact stress prediction of a total knee replacement tibial tray under physiological loading conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can identify worst-case contact stress distributions for a Class II orthopedic implant at Model Risk Level 3. Full 13-factor assessment: all factors either assessed at or above required levels or formally scoped out with documented rationale. Conforms to ProfileComplete.",
